    <p class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12" style="color:#003D7A;">We are a fully mobile dog grooming service operating throughout Newcastle, Gateshead and Durham. Serving happy hounds since the year 2000.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl" style="background:#EBF3FB;border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🚐</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color:#001F3D;">We Come to You</h3>
        <p style="color:#003D7A;">A fully mobile service that comes to your home, saving you time and the hassle of dropping off and collecting your pet.</p>
      </div>
