        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✨</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color:#001F3D;">Groomed in Our Van</h3>
        <p style="color:#003D7A;">Unlike most other mobile grooming services, your dog is groomed inside our state of the art mobile grooming van. Your house stays spotless.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl" style="background:#EBF3FB;border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🐶</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color:#001F3D;">One to One Attention</h3>
        <p style="color:#003D7A;">Quick, convenient and all done within an hour. With one to one attention your dog remains calm and gets the TLC they deserve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

