        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Bath</h3>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color:#003D7A;">A thorough wash with quality shampoo, leaving your dog clean, fresh and smelling great.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-3">✂️</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Clip</h3>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color:#003D7A;">A professional clip suited to your dog's breed and coat type, keeping them comfortable and tidy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-3">💅</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Nail Trim</h3>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color:#003D7A;">Safe and careful nail trimming to keep your dog comfortable and prevent any discomfort.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
